# Data Collection and Dataset

The project used publicly available NHS England and NHS Digital datasets collected between 2016 and 2023.

## Dataset Characteristics

* 88 variables
* 704 observations
* longitudinal NHS operational data

## Included Variables

### Operational Metrics

* A&E waiting times
* total attendances
* patients waiting over four hours
* bed occupancy levels
* available hospital beds
* workforce statistics

### Demographic Variables

* age groups
* gender
* ethnicity
* deprivation levels

### Department Variables

* Type 1 Consultant-led A&E
* Type 2 Single-specialty A&E
* Type 3 & 4 Minor Injury Units

