# Data Preprocessing

Data cleaning and preprocessing were conducted using Microsoft Excel and R.

The preprocessing workflow included:

* compiling datasets from multiple NHS sources
* handling missing values
* restructuring variables into broader analytical categories
* transforming variables for non-linear regression analysis
* correlation assessment
* time-series preparation

Several R packages were used including:

* dplyr
* tidyr
* ggplot2
* forecast
* tseries

The dependent variable representing patients waiting over four hours was log-transformed prior to regression analysis.

