# Limitations

Several limitations affected the project:

* reliance on secondary NHS data
* limited access to individual-level patient information
* inability to assess qualitative staff experiences
* operational variables difficult to quantify consistently
* forecasting uncertainty due to changing healthcare conditions

Despite these limitations, the project provided meaningful operational and predictive insights into NHS emergency department performance.

